name: Avoiding
description: This still life work comes from the the series published in L'Officiel. Presented cinemagraph was a complementary part of the printed story. For the context and meaning of this creation, you can view the full publication with description at https://annczerny.pl/avoiding. Cinemagraph - an art work, where only one part of the image is moving, the rest is staying still.
